Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道您要在這片黑暗之中召喚魔王之夜Death嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.82,0:02:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道您把時間停止了Death嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.80,0:02:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像也不是這樣Death呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:02:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:03:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 主人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.69,0:03:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人對凸守…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人 這樣不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凸守是主人的隨從
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能對您抱有非分之想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 世間有多少人抵擋不住禁果的誘惑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和勇太擁抱過了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.99,0:03:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.79,0:03:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡勇太！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你是冒牌貨？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到繼森大人之後 連主人都被山寨了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.94,0:03:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.86,0:03:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.49,0:03:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.84,0:03:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜…喜歡上了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漆黑烈火使？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.13,0:04:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人 凸守有事要辦 先行告退Death
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.80,0:04:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凸守…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.44,0:04:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別阻止我Death
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.72,0:04:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為隨從 我一定要親手把主人的偷心賊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人說過 「多虧漆黑烈火使的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.93,0:04:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,邪王真眼能守護到如今」Death
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.03,0:04:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.69,0:04:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這份強烈的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定能傳達給漆黑烈火使Death
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.28,0:04:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我服侍了主人兩年有餘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.61,0:04:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經了解主人的一切Death咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凸守
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.53,0:04:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無需擔心Death
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,邪王真眼是最強Death
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.18,0:05:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會順利Death的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你和小鳥遊同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我該怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.01,0:05:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.53,0:05:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我應該跟她告白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡小鳥遊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.73,0:05:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.07,0:05:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 但不是因為她身材好或是可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢…她雖然中二得無可救藥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但卻不是單純的中二病
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她也有自己的煩惱 也很可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不 也不是在同情她…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說了 別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.06,0:05:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡上一個人是不需要理由的哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這句你沒資格說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.86,0:05:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噁心死了噁心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:05:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難得我肯聽你傾訴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.62,0:06:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰想找你傾訴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「如果不說的話 我就在班裡散布謠言」這句話是你說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 嘿～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說 你的運氣真好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.58,0:06:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊的實力位居 可愛女生錦標賽第四名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種事 總有一天會做那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.83,0:06:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉勇太 我沒有關於肉體接觸的經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.65,0:06:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.88,0:06:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼這算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋嗎你是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.95,0:06:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我也去…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.70,0:06:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞定一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茴香學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請和我一起參加後夜祭！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:06:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.57,0:06:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:07:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我一定要看你們的肥皂劇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.13,0:07:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這才不是演戲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.41,0:07:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說 你為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天的即興表演要先排練啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,富樫同學和小鳥遊同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別談這個話題Death
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凸守現在很不爽Death
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.48,0:07:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想揍人Death
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在可沒時間陪你胡鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.45,0:07:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 把那兩人……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人回去了Death
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人一起！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.22,0:07:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.31,0:07:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漆黑烈火使說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「有重要的事要談」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.79,0:07:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就把她帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.79,0:07:31.93,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.94,0:07:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵從吾之契約 聽從吾命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.92,0:07:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵從吾之契約 聽從吾命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.71,0:08:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵從吾之契約 聽從吾命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.42,0:08:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔導石
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以實現願望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.39,0:08:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凸守給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,願望？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,願望的內容我可不會說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.58,0:08:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…我也沒問
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔導石接收到強烈的願望會發熱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.97,0:08:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.31,0:08:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你帶傘了…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要說的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.38,0:09:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的…我也有話想對勇太說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.24,0:09:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關係到最高機密的重要的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.84,0:09:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.95,0:09:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也有話… 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.79,0:09:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.40,0:09:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能一直這樣耗下去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.07,0:09:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 漆黑原罪音速II
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.07,0:09:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(659,650)}Schwarzsechs Prototype Mk II
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.76,0:09:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全名說得真流利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.05,0:09:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒掉到河裡面真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.09,0:09:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.92,0:09:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.09,0:10:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光在流動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.78,0:10:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花…
Comment: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:17.33,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,IN
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fnDFPOYoJun-W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}何も言わない背中に対して
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.48,0:10:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fnDFPOYoJun-W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}なんて言えばいいのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.16,0:10:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fnDFPOYoJun-W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}好きになるのに理由はないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.22,0:10:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fnDFPOYoJun-W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}勇気の無さに言い訳ばかり
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fnDFPOYoJun-W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}「流星群を眺めていたら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fnDFPOYoJun-W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}キラキラって音がするみたい。」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.60,0:10:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fnDFPOYoJun-W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}そういう気持ちの余韻すら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fnDFPOYoJun-W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}君となら分かち合える
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.86,0:10:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fnDFPOYoJun-W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}恋の欠片が　いま一つに…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fnDFPOYoJun-W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}安っぽい言葉で飾っても
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fnDFPOYoJun-W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}君に届かないかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fnDFPOYoJun-W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}でも何も言わないままだと君が
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fnDFPOYoJun-W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}消えちゃうかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fnDFPOYoJun-W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}あの星みたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.92,0:11:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fnDFPOYoJun-W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}今どこで泣いてるの?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fnDFPOYoJun-W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}どうしたら笑ってくれますか?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fnDFPOYoJun-W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}点を繋いで星座にしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fnDFPOYoJun-W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}その指で
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fnDFPOYoJun-W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}背中合わせじゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.36,0:11:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fnDFPOYoJun-W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}こっちを向いて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.96,0:11:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fnDFPOYoJun-W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}そして隣を歩きたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fn華康歐陽詢體W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}能感受到背靠背的溫度 卻聽不到你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.48,0:10:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fn華康歐陽詢體W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}看不到你的臉龐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.16,0:10:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fn華康歐陽詢體W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}喜歡你 卻找不到任何理由
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.22,0:10:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fn華康歐陽詢體W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}只能不斷地掩飾自己的膽怯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fn華康歐陽詢體W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}眺望著流星群
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fn華康歐陽詢體W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}閃閃發亮 在演奏愛的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.60,0:10:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fn華康歐陽詢體W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}心中的餘韻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fn華康歐陽詢體W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}與你靈犀相通
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.86,0:10:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fn華康歐陽詢體W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}你我的星空 融為一體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fn華康歐陽詢體W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}也許你無法讀懂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fn華康歐陽詢體W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}我生硬隱晦的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fn華康歐陽詢體W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}如果選擇繼續沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fn華康歐陽詢體W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}你也許就會消失無蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fn華康歐陽詢體W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}如同那流星一般
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.92,0:11:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fn華康歐陽詢體W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}苦苦尋找流淚的你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fn華康歐陽詢體W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}為了你的笑容絞盡腦汁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fn華康歐陽詢體W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}像那連點成線永不分離的星座一般
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fn華康歐陽詢體W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}握著你的指尖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fn華康歐陽詢體W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}撲進我的懷裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.36,0:11:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fn華康歐陽詢體W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.96,0:11:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\fn華康歐陽詢體W5\an7\fad(300,300)\1c&HF278AF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord3}相互偎依著共度下半生
Comment: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.45,0:10:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.82,0:10:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.64,0:10:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.45,0:10:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等 等下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這應該由我來說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,邪王真眼已經決定是我先說了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是漆黑烈火使啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.03,0:10:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,邪王真眼是最強的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.62,0:10:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不算不算
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.15,0:11:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易想出來的 要說了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被黑暗烈火包圍之人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與漆黑烈火訂下戀人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不弄了 總之…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.56,0:11:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.29,0:11:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.09,0:11:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇太！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被黑暗烈火包圍之人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與漆黑烈火使訂下戀人之契約吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.65,0:11:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候一般不是躺在懷裡的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.27,0:11:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害羞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小拇指的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就…小拇指
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.91,0:12:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.61,0:12:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 好晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.98,0:12:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 樟葉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.26,0:12:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原告對被告有愛意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我現在只想盡快跟被告劃清界限
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在鬧什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有話跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,味道又不如以前了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.59,0:12:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能在家裡說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.15,0:12:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為不能讓六花聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.53,0:13:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從義大利總店寄來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.51,0:13:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,邀請我去深造
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.91,0:13:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有理由拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.29,0:13:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前在懷疑我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛～算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是這不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花也肯定…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不能讓她一個人住在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.12,0:13:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以讓媽媽代替我和她一起住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花的媽媽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼想…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼想…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得會順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花並不是討厭媽媽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.83,0:13:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…嘗試了很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.34,0:13:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隱瞞爸爸的事情也道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.26,0:13:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了 十花姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.14,0:14:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說的話 她肯定會聽的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只要對她說 「變得正常點吧！」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.48,0:14:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花已經很正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.14,0:14:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個眼罩對她來說 只是自衛的盔甲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想 六花肯定也知道… 這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是心裡有個怎麼也跨不過去的坎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.02,0:14:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用那個姿態 獲得保護…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保護什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不想讓這一切就這樣終結
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.60,0:14:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽十花姐或媽媽的話 全盤接受的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.80,0:14:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切就會結束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不想這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.96,0:14:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結束又有什麼不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,境界線也好 邪王真眼也好 都是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.17,0:14:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管她怎麼尋找 都無法再見到爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.88,0:15:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,認同她說的話 能解決什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.49,0:15:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她所追求的東西是永遠無法得到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,認同這些行為 太不負責任了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來 歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.55,0:15:31.20,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,起司焗烤馬鈴薯一份 多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.02,0:15:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人氣好高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.61,0:15:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別看她們這麼甜美香脆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,內部的人際關係可是錯綜複雜的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才不幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.36,0:15:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 所以外表甜美香脆內部錯綜複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟起司焗烤馬鈴薯一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼漂亮話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說 富樫同學和小鳥遊同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去換衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.98,0:15:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.90,0:15:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.98,0:15:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上用即興表演把觀眾全搶過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.25,0:16:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這不是森大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別叫我森大…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.28,0:16:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.01,0:16:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有鈴木
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.26,0:16:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 初中後第一次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.37,0:16:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您現在貴庚啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.87,0:16:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,716歲？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.76,0:16:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在還在抓蜥蜴嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤不也是把嘴唇塗成紫色來裝病嬌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 佐藤還做過這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.45,0:16:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鈴木也說過發現了妖精之類的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.91,0:16:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妖精…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.75,0:16:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道她們在較什麼勁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中二病的諷刺挖苦 真是危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒決出勝負Death哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我把錘子的威力提高了4倍De…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.88,0:16:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好重Death
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是笨得沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.22,0:17:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,認同她說的話 能解決什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.63,0:17:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,認同這些行為 太不負責任了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.32,0:17:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇太 好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.78,0:17:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別兩眼放光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,技能 被黑暗之火擁抱著邁向消亡吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇太 做給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.78,0:17:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明馬上就要做了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.76,0:17:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛～ 話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.12,0:17:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被黑暗之火擁抱著邁向消亡唄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.55,0:17:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有威力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西怎麼會有威力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.77,0:17:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,張開雙腿 扎馬步 甩動披風的下端
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.30,0:17:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.35,0:17:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被黑暗之火擁抱著邁向消亡吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.35,0:17:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別拍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.94,0:17:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任務差不多要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:17:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各就各位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 雖然不太情願呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.46,0:18:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.01,0:18:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.56,0:18:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小拇指
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.03,0:18:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問 這裡有沒有叫小鳥遊六花的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 她是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.21,0:18:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她現在去了別的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.92,0:18:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請把這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.26,0:18:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.80,0:18:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 我現在就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.81,0:18:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是不太想見我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.59,0:19:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.05,0:19:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不負責任的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.62,0:19:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.27,0:19:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡發什麼呆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.89,0:19:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始表演吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.32,0:19:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在正好來了很多客人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.03,0:19:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把眼罩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.95,0:19:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摘下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:43.55,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 每年慣例的才藝大會開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.96,0:19:46.27,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎中途參加哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.31,0:19:50.33,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼讓我們馬上開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.74,0:19:52.12,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,有請一號選手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.41,0:19:54.52,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,一號 二年三班 原田真也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:55.60,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,表演人物模仿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.89,0:19:56.76,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,教務主任！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:19:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即興表演結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.60,0:20:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我和那個中二屁孩勉強撐過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她可真是下狠手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.99,0:20:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真意外…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.13,0:20:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然會說那種話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.07,0:20:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個便當
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.56,0:20:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有些餘溫…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是沉甸甸地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.56,0:20:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塞滿了 滿滿的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.66,0:20:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.10,0:20:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現實
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.38,0:20:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二號 一年四班 一色誠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表演嘶吼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五月七日茴香學姐！ 請和我交往！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.57,0:20:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.17,0:20:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 小鳥遊同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,富樫同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這樣滿好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:20:55.68,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝一色誠同學的精彩表演
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.72,0:20:58.47,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請中途參加的這位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:21:00.27,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,請戴眼罩的這位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.33,0:21:02.66,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,一年四班 小鳥遊六花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.43,0:21:04.30,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,表演唱歌
Comment: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:08.68,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,IN
